This section constitutes the Overall Software Test Report as required by
EN 50716:2023, Clause 7.7 and Table A.1 (document 24). It records the results
of executing the software validation test cases defined in the Software
Validation Test Specification against the source code baseline identified in
05_component_impl_test.sdoc (CI-010), on the target or representative platform
used for final system-level testing.
<<<

